deftms ~>>>ARETE 'edges of a mesh treated by hashing i.e. the position of the
edge is the sum of its vertex numbers or a chaining to the next edge'
variable muet DATE 'date of creation of the TMS'   reel2  ;
variable muet NUTD 'number of the descriptor array TD' entier ; 
variable MOARET 'number of integers for each edge'  entier ;
variable MXARET 'max number of edges'             entier ; 
variable NBARFB 'total number of boundary edges'  entier ;
variable L1ARFB 'number first boundary edge NOT on a line' entier ;
variable NBARIN 'total number of interface edges'          entier ;
variable L1ARIN 'number of the first interface edge NOT on a line' entier ; 
variable NBARTG 'number of edges with tangent vectors'     entier ;
variable NUMILF 'min number of the lines of the surface' entier ;
variable NUMXLF 'max number of the lines of the surface' entier ;
tableau L1LGFR(NUMILF..NUMXLF) 'number of the first edge of a boundary line'
        entier ;
tableau LARETE(1..MOARET,1..MXARET)
'st1,st2,link,fe1,fe2,internal or boundary edge next number tg edge' entier ;
tableau NUTGAR(1..2,1..NBARTG) 'numbers of the 2 tangents of the edges' entier ;
fintms ;


For memory :

If NUMXLF=0 
then NO array L1LGFR     case of a mesh with only the NSEF TMS
Else case of an object mesh with TOPOLOGIE + NPEF"... TMS

If NBARTG=0 Then NO array NUTGAR
